data.description: Don't miss out on this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a spacious - open floor plan great for entertaining in California City.   The location is perfect for military who work on base at Edwards!  This home is situated on a quiet cul-de-sac away from main roads.  The home has been newly painted inside and the kitchen has been recently remodeled with new cupboards and counter tops!   cupboards and garage access.  The front yard is landscaped with artificial turf and zero  maintenance. The back yard is fully fenced.  There is a Tesla solar lease that needs to be assumed by buyer - the cost is approximately $120 a month.
